biography:
The greatest celebration of Star Wars in the galaxy!
🗓 April 1-4, 2027
📍 Los Angeles, California

latestIgtvVideos.caption: Thank you all for being the best part of the 𝘚𝘵𝘢𝘳 𝘞𝘢𝘳𝘴 Celebration experience! At #SWCE we saw a community of fans come together to enjoy all things 𝘚𝘵𝘢𝘳 𝘞𝘢𝘳𝘴 and we can’t wait to do it all again in 2025. May the 4th be with you!

@citizenwatchus will be at #StarWarsCelebration with special announcements and new releases, only happening this weekend. Here’s a sneak peak of an exclusive collection of watches, with a new model released each day at the Citizen booth.

latestPosts.caption: Today, the Force is strong with everyone 💛 We miss you already and are looking forward to celebrating the first 50 years of Star Wars together in 2027!
latestPosts.alt: Photo by Star Wars Celebration on May 04, 2025. May be an image of poster, costume, sword and text that says 'MAY THE 4TH BEWITH BE YOU!'.

latestPosts.caption: Explore officially licensed high-end STAR WARS costumes, helmets, and collectables from Denuo Novo with products from across the saga!

latestPosts.caption: We've spent three amazing days celebrating the greatest galaxy with the greatest fans. Thank you to every Jedi, Sith, rebel, bounty hunter, and droid who made us all feel a little closer. We can't wait to do it again in Los Angeles. 🩷💚💜

latestPosts.caption: Day 3 at Star Wars Celebration is going full lightspeed! Cosplays are elite, the vibes are strong, and the fans? Bringing more fire than a twin-sun Tatooine sunset. From Mandalorians to Jedi Masters, you've all leveled up this weekend. One more day in the galaxy to go—let’s see what the final chapter brings! #SWCJ
